(456, 'next festival video labaratorija', 'Jauni videomeno kûrëjai, ieðkantys idëju ir norintys iðmokti jas realizuoti kvieèiami dalyvauti Next Festival videolaboratorijoje.  Ji nebus orientuota á technines þinias, uþsiëmimuose vyraus kûrybinis akcentas. Pagrindinis klausimas, á kurá bus bandoma ieðkoti atsakymo  susitikimø metu: kaip idëja virsta kûriniu?', 'Kartu bus mokomasi filmuoti, redaguoti medþiagà kompiuteriu naudojantis Adobe Premiere" programa bei perkelti filmukà á DVD diskà.<br><br>Next Festival videolaboratorijà ves Martin John Callanan ið garsaus Londono Slade elektroniniø medijø centro. Laboratorijoje sukurti darbai bus pristatyti festivalio metu.<br><br>Norintiems dalyvauti reikalingos bendrosios anglø kalbos þinios.Galimybë naudotis videokamera ir kompiuterine áranga bus privalumais organizatoriams svarstant kandidatus. <br><br>Norintys dalyvauti atsakymus á ðiuos klausimus iki vasario 23 dienos turi siøsti elektroniniu paðtu info@nextfestival.net<br> 1. Name<br> 2. Age <br> 3. Contact email and phone number<br> 4. Previous visual experiences you want to tell us about<br> 5. Do you mind working in a group? Is there a specific person applying to the workshop you would like to work with? <br> 6. Do you have access to the computer with editing software (Adobe Premiere)? <br> 7. Do you have a digital video camera you could use for the workshop? <br> 8. Do you have any ideas to bring to the workshop? <br> 9. Complete the sentence If I could delete any film that was previously made IINSERT INTO `avnews` (`id`, `subject`, `info`, `full_text`, `posted`, `keywords`, `visible`, `category_id`, `file`, `submiter`, `authorizer`, `auth_date`) VALUES
